OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780570971
OL,3,CCouncil ad banned for 'misleading'
OL,4,Cdomestic fire pollution claim
OL,6,FSmall text at the bottom of the ad
OL,7,Fstated: "City sensor data comparing
OL,8,FDecember 2024 to April 2025 with May
OL,9,F2025 to November 2025 at Middle
OL,10,FStreet, Elm Grove Primary, Adlington
OL,11,FPrimary and Saltdean Primary schools."
OL,13,FTwo complainants, including the owner
OL,14,Fof a chimney sweeping business, said
OL,15,Fthe ad misleadingly implied that the
OL,16,Fuse of wood burners and open fires was
OL,17,Fthe cause of the claimed increase in
OL,18,Fparticle pollution.
OL,26,@oD@IOUsD@fO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
