OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780570971
OL,3,CCouncil ad banned for 'misleading'
OL,4,Cdomestic fire pollution claim
OL,6,FBrighton & Hove City Council said the
OL,7,Fad was part of a campaign to raise
OL,8,Fawareness of the damaging impact of
OL,9,Fparticulate matter (PM) pollution from
OL,10,Fdomestic wood burning, including open
OL,11,Ffires and wood burners.
OL,13,FThey compared pollution levels in two
OL,14,Fparts of the year ` one covering
OL,15,Fwinter months when wood burners and
OL,16,Fopen fires were used more often and
OL,17,Fthe other covering the warmer April to
OL,18,FOctober.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780570971
OL,3,CCouncil ad banned for 'misleading'
OL,4,Cdomestic fire pollution claim
OL,6,FAcross all eight monitoring sites
OL,7,FPM2.5 (particulate matter with a
OL,8,Fdiameter of 2.5 micrometres or less)
OL,9,Fpollution was 91% higher in period one
OL,10,Fthan period two.
OL,12,FThe same results showed a 79% increase
OL,13,Facross the four primary schools
OL,14,Fbetween the two periods.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
