PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780570971
OL,3,CCouncil ad banned for 'misleading'
OL,4,Cdomestic fire pollution claim
OL,6,FThe Advertising Standards Authority
OL,7,F(ASA) said the ad implied there was a
OL,8,Fdirect causal link between the use of
OL,9,Fwood burners and open fires, and the
OL,10,Fclaimed increase in particulate
OL,11,Fpollution, and that those heat sources
OL,12,Fwere the sole cause of the increase.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
