OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780570971
OL,3,CCouncil ad banned for 'misleading'
OL,4,Cdomestic fire pollution claim
OL,6,FIt said: "While we understood domestic
OL,7,Fwood burning was a significant
OL,8,Fcontributor to urban PM2.5 emissions,
OL,9,Fwe had not seen evidence in support of
OL,10,Fthe direct link claimed in the ad."
OL,12,FThe ASA found that additional evidence
OL,13,Fsupplied by the council did not make
OL,14,Ffindings on the claimed increase in
OL,15,Fparticulate pollution at the primary
OL,16,Fschools referenced in the ad.
OL,26,@nD@JOUrD@cO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780570971
OL,3,CCouncil ad banned for 'misleading'
OL,4,Cdomestic fire pollution claim
OL,6,FThe ASA concluded: "The ad implied
OL,7,Fthat wood burners and open fires were
OL,8,Fthe cause of the claimed increase in
OL,9,Fparticulate pollution around four city
OL,10,Fprimary schools.
OL,12,F"However, we had not seen evidence to
OL,13,Fsubstantiate the claim. We therefore
OL,14,Fconcluded the ad was likely to
OL,15,Fmislead."
OL,26,@nD@TOUtD@AOUwD@IO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
