OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780570971
OL,3,CCouncil ad banned for 'misleading'
OL,4,Cdomestic fire pollution claim
OL,6,FBanning the ad, the ASA said: "We told
OL,7,FBrighton & Hove City Council to ensure
OL,8,Fthat robust evidence was held to
OL,9,Fsubstantiate any claims where a direct
OL,10,Fcausal link between the use of wood
OL,11,Fburners and open fires and an increase
OL,12,Fin particle pollution was stated or
OL,13,Fimplied."
OL,26,@nD@_OUuD@IO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
