OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780570971
OL,3,CCouncil ad banned for 'misleading'
OL,4,Cdomestic fire pollution claim
OL,6,FCouncillor Tim Rowkins, cabinet member
OL,7,Ffor net zero and environmental
OL,8,Fservices at Brighton & Hove City
OL,9,FCouncil, said: "We have clear and
OL,10,Fdetailed local data that shows the
OL,11,Fimpact that burning solid fuels has on
OL,12,Fair quality in our densely populated
OL,13,Furban areas.
OL,15,F"The ASA has ruled that, in one of the
OL,16,Fcampaign graphics we used, there was
OL,17,Fan insufficiently clear link to the
OL,18,Fevidence. There was no ruling against
OL,19,Fthe campaign as a whole, or the other
OL,20,Fmaterials that were used.
OL,26,@qD@POUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
